creator: Studentenschaft der Universität St. Gallen
descriptionHtml:
Its aim is to centralise information around the HSG campus and facilitate your life on campus. This project was initiated for the 100-year anniversary of the SHSG. We have included the following features:

- Home page with announcements, news and events around campus
- Seat finder
- Nearby buses and trains
- Mensa menu
- Club channels with the 130+ clubs at HSG!
- Club news and events
- Marketplace because Sharing is Caring
- Login with your HSG account
- Map of HSG
- Room booking system
- Compass mailbox (so when you receive you grades, you can directly check them there)
- Grades and achievements
- Unisport program
- Library books finder (Swisscovery)
And more to come…

If you have any questions or suggestions about the app, do not hesitate to reach out to us !

This project was launched by Ali Jouini, Vice-President of the SHSG 2020/21 and developed by Hugo Casademont.
